# Changelog

All notable changes to **4Term** will be documented in this file.

## [1.0.0] - 2025-06-15

### Added
 - Initial release of **4Term**

## [1.1.0] - 2025-06-17

### Added
 - DTR and RTS control in the menu strip
 - Auto macro sending feature
 
### Changed
 - Main form layout and design
 - Serial options form 
 - Settings form
 - Macro set styling
 - XML file handling
 - Serial port handling
 - Settings handling

## [1.2.0] - 2025-06-24
 
### Changed
 - Removed unused code and redundant comments
 - Refactored functions for better readability and efficiency
 - Simplified assembly attribute accessors with helper methods
 - Improved naming conventions and consistent formatting
 - Updated comments for clarity and better documentation
 - Removed deprecated methods and fixed minor bugs

## [1.3.0] - 2025-07-02

### Added
 - AutoUpdater

